<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 2. Ocular lines: a present, Pachybrachis peccans b small, Pachybrachis hepaticus c absent, Pachybrachis spumarius." , "Habitus 10. Dorsal habitus of Pachybrachis obsoletus. Scale bar, 1 mm." , "Figure 7. Elytral punctures and coloration: a in rows in deep striae, Pachybrachis luctuosus b confused in basal half, in rows in apical half, Pachybrachis calcaratus c all confused, Pachybrachis hepaticus d confused and mottled, Pachybrachis spumarius e vittate with marginal vitta interrupted, Pachybrachis bivattatus f black, margined with yellow, Pachybrachis nigriconis carbonarius g entirely black, Pachybrachis luridus." , "Figure 6. Pronotum: a reddish, with close-up of marginal bead, Pachybrachis bivittatus b mottled, Pachybrachis spumarius c with black M-mark, Pachybrachis m-nigrum d almost black, Pachybrachis nigricornis carbonarius." , "Habitus 14. Dorsal habitus of Pachybrachis spumarius. Scale bar, 1 mm." , "Habitus 1. Dorsal habitus of Pachybrachis atomarius. Scale bar, 1 mm." , "Habitus 11. Dorsal habitus of Pachybrachis othonus othonus. Scale bar, 1 mm." , "Habitus 6. Dorsal habitus of Pachybrachis luctuosus. Scale bar, 1 mm." , "Figure 8. Pygidium: a largely yellow, Pachybrachis bivittatus b with well-defined yellow spots, Pachybrachis cephalicus c with faint reddish spots, Pachybrachis spumarius d black, Pachybrachis atomarius." , "Figure 3. Front femora: a not enlarged, Pachybrachis hepaticus b thickened, Pachybrachis peccans." , "Habitus 9 b. Dorsal habitus of Pachybrachis nigricornis carbonarius. Almost black. Scale bar, 1 mm." , "Figure 10. Aedeagus: a lateral view, Pachybrachis luctuosus b lateral view, Pachybrachis spumarius c apex, dorsal view, Pachybrachis spumarius." , "Habitus 5. Dorsal habitus of Pachybrachis hepaticus hepaticus. Scale bar, 1 mm." , "Habitus 17. Dorsal habitus of Pachybrachis trinotatus. Scale bar, 1 mm." , "Figure 1. Eyes: a close eyes, Pachybrachis pectoralis b normal eyes, Pachybrachis peccans c normal eyes and yellow face, male Pachybrachis atomarius d remote eyes, Pachybrachis hepaticus." , "Figure 9. Sexes: a male abdomen, ventral view, Pachybrachis bivittatus b female abdomen, ventral view, Pachybrachis bivittatus." , "Figure 5. Tibial spurs: a absent from front leg, Pachybrachis atomarius b minute on front leg, Pachybrachis spumarius c large on front leg, Pachybrachis calcaratus d small and pointed on middle legs in most species." , "Habitus 15. Dorsal habitus of Pachybrachis subfasciatus. Scale bar, 1 mm." , "Habitus 4. Dorsal habitus of Pachybrachis cephalicus. Scale bar, 1 mm." , "Habitus 16. Dorsal habitus of Pachybrachis tridens. Scale bar, 1 mm." , "Figure 4. Claws: a, b front claws enlarged c, d normal." , "Habitus 2. Dorsal habitus of Pachybrachis bivittatus. Scale bar, 1 mm." , "Habitus 9 a. Dorsal habitus of Pachybrachis nigricornis difficilis. Scale bar, 1 mrn." , "Habitus 12. Dorsal habitus of Pachybrachis peccans. Scale bar, 1 mn." , "Habitus 13. Dorsal habitus of Pachybrachis pectoralis. Scale bar, 1 mm." , "Habitus 7. Dorsal habitus of Pachybrachis luridus. Scale bar, 1 mm." , "Habitus 8. Dorsal habitus of Pachybrachis m-nigrum. Scale bar, 1 mm." , "Habitus 3. Dorsal habitus of Pachybrachis calcaratus. Scale bar, 1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20862" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20859" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20920" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20914" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20923" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20926" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20860" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20917" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20863" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20866" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20869" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20919" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20912" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20921" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20924" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20906" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20861" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20915" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20908" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20864" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20867" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20858" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20910" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20922" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20904" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20913" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20916" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20925" .

